  "body": "If the rook-operator pod is recreated it gets stuck in a loop trying to create another TPR.\r\n\r\n```\r\n2017-03-13 13:32:12.392785 I | rook-operator: starting operator in namespace rook\r\n2017-03-13 13:32:12.392999 I | operator: creating rook TPR\r\n2017-03-13 13:32:12.449403 E | operator: failed to create tpr. failed to create TPR. thirdpartyresources.extensions \"cluster.rook.io\" already exists. retrying...\r\n```\r\n\r\nFor now deleting the TPR resumes normal operation.\r\n```\r\nkubectl delete thirdpartyresource cluster.rook.io\r\n```",
